headline: KeyBanc upgrades Rockwell Automation, raises targets for Emerson, WESCO
summary: Investing.com -- KeyBanc upgraded Rockwell Automation Inc (NYSE:ROK) to "overweight" and raised price targets for Emerson Electric Company (NYSE:EMR) and WESCO International amid stabilisation in automation markets.
